au.gov.ansto.bragg.process.port
Interface Tuner

All Superinterfaces:
au.gov.ansto.bragg.base.common.All, Common, au.gov.ansto.bragg.base.common.Publisher, java.io.Serializable
public interface Tuner
extends Common

A child class of Port to tune the Var ports.

A Tuner port is build upon a processor framework object to tune the Var ports of the processors in the framework. Since Var ports are not exposed to developer users. User can use a Tuner object to access and tune the Var port.

When an Tuner port object is created, it is configured to be able to take certain type of signal information, for example, an Integer, a Double or a double array.
